file_content.text: I stopped his last wish before. Now I put it back!
--final message. The Nightmare Lands have begun to seriously affect my mind.
I do not recommend sending initiates here. Let them train to resist the Force somewhere else--
--leaving for the shrine tonight. The prophecy is ready--
--the Voss believe in martyrs, and I'll play this role to the end. Give "Hunter" my love.
Transmit. Activate destruct sequence.
I stopped it last time. This time, we all burn.
You can burn if you want. I'm taking that data and leaving.
I'm not that easy to kill.
Dying here is pointless. Hand over the data and come with me.
We can get out together.
Ha! Ha....
I can do without your opinion. But I'll take your data.
Shut up. [Kill him]
Come on, let's move!
Agent, we should leave.
Ready to go, sir.
Perhaps it's time we left, hmm?
The ship is built for atomic annihilation. My core systems may survive, but you will not.
Okay, that's not supposed to be here. I think the Shining Man came this way.
The Shining Man... he must have flown into the Nightmare Lands and landed here.
The Shining Man stored his ship here. This is how he came to Voss!
The Shining Man's ship. Where better to hide it than the most dangerous place on Voss?
The starship belonged to my benefactors. You continue to follow their trail.
You are not worthy to speak.
